2:T6fb,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Nanonets better than Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Nanonets scores 7.0 overall while Rossum scores 7.0. Nanonets is best for finance teams and accounts payable, while Rossum excels for enterprises and logistics."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Nanonets or Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Nanonets starts at Free and Rossum starts at Custom. Nanonets offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Nanonets to Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Nanonets and Rossum support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Nanonets vs Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Nanonets holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Rossum has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 5/10. Users praise Nanonets for excellent ocr and data extraction accuracy and Rossum for high accuracy on structured documents."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Nanonets or Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Nanonets for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Rossum remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize high accuracy on structured documents. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-head